# Raw uploaded files and cached extracted text - not source-controlled.
# /index/ and /db/ ARE committed on purpose: Railway only deploys this git repo,
# and Notes/the handbook PDF live one level up (outside the repo, never pushed),
# so the index has to ship pre-built rather than rebuilt on the server. Rerun
# build_index.py locally and commit the result whenever source content changes.
/files/
/cache/
